    public interface IFixListener
extends Remote, EventListener, Serializable
    This interface defines the methods that are called on any listener to Fix.

    Each call back method contains compID, subID and locationID's corresponding to the FIX session that originated the event. Using these values it is possible for a single listener instance to process events from multiple different systems.
